#GitHub
#It is a Version Control System or Source Code Management

#Types Version Control System
	#Local
	#Centralized
	#Distributed
	
#git is a type of Distributed version conrol system

#Features of git
	#Works on distributed system
	#compatiable with all operating system
	#non-linear development
	#brancing
	#reliable
	
	
